race.comment: MICHIGA (7) returns after 12 weeks in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a eighth over 1509m at Lone Star Park (Turf). Set to return in style. JAWDROPPER (8) debuted four weeks ago when she finished fourth over 1006m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt), beaten 8 lengths. Will improve and looks well placed. BRUNCH SPOT (4) was in contention on the bend and finished second last start over 1207m at this track (Dirt), beaten 5.5 lengths. Must raise the bar but this looks well within her grasp. CIVILIANAIRE (12) didn't do a lot on debut eight weeks ago, finishing 51 lengths from the winner in sixth over 1609m at Ellis Park (Dirt). Plenty of scope for improvement. Can improve.
